#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "Working with the &kappname; editor"
msgstr "Delo z &kappname; urednik"

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "Pregled"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kappname; editor is the editing area of the &kappname; window. This "
"editor is shared between &kate; and &kwrite;, and it can also be used in "
"&konqueror; for displaying text files from your local computer, or from the "
"network."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; urejevalnik je področje urejanja datoteke &kappname; okno. Ta "
"urejevalnik si delita &kate; in &kwrite;, uporablja pa se lahko tudi v "
"&konqueror; za prikaz besedilnih datotek iz vašega lokalnega računalnika ali "
"iz omrežja."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid "The editor is composed of the following components:"
msgstr "Urejevalnik je sestavljen iz naslednjih komponent:"

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid "The editing area"
msgstr "Območje urejanja"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is where the text of your document is located."
msgstr "Tukaj se nahaja besedilo vašega dokumenta."

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Scrollbars"
msgstr "Drsni trakovi"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The scrollbars indicate the position of the visible part of the document "
"text, and can be used to move around the document. Dragging the scrollbars "
"will not cause the insertion cursor to be moved."
msgstr ""
"Drsni trakovi označujejo položaj vidnega dela besedila dokumenta in se lahko "
"uporabljajo za premikanje po dokumentu. Vlečenje drsnih trakov ne bo "
"povzročilo premikanja kazalca za vstavljanje."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid "The scrollbars are displayed and hidden as required."
msgstr "Drsni trakovi so po potrebi prikazani in skriti."

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Icon Border"
msgstr "Meja ikone"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The icon border is a small pane on the left side of the editor, displaying a "
"small icon next to marked lines."
msgstr ""
"Obroba ikone je majhno podokno na levi strani urejevalnika, ki prikazuje "
"majhno ikono poleg označenih vrstic."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can set or remove a <link linkend=\"kate-part-bookmarks\">bookmark</"
"link> in a visible line by clicking the &LMB; in the icon border next to "
"that line."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-part-bookmarks\">Zaznamek</link> lahko nastavite ali "
"odstranite v vidni vrstici tako, da kliknete &LMB; na obrobi ikone poleg te "
"vrstice."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The display of the icon border can be toggled using the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Icon Border</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Prikaz obrobe ikone lahko preklopite z menijsko postavko "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži obrobo ikone</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Line Numbers Pane"
msgstr "Podokno s številkami vrstic"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Line numbers pane shows the line numbers of all visible lines in the "
"document."
msgstr ""
"Podokno Številke vrstic prikazuje številke vrstic vseh vidnih vrstic v "
"dokumentu."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The display of the Line Numbers Pane can be toggled using the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Line Numbers</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Prikaz podokna s številkami vrstic lahko preklapljate z menijsko postavko "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prikaži številke vrstic</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Folding Pane"
msgstr "Zložljivo podokno"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The folding pane allows you to collapse or expand foldable blocks of lines. "
"The calculation of the foldable regions is done according to rules in the "
"syntax highlight definition for the document."
msgstr ""
"Zložljivo podokno vam omogoča, da strnete ali razširite zložljive bloke črt. "
"Izračun prepogljivih območij se izvede v skladu s pravili v definiciji "
"poudarjanja sintakse za dokument."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid "Also in this Chapter:"
msgstr "Tudi v tem poglavju:"

#. Tag: link
#: part.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"kate-part-navigation\">Navigating in the Text</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"kate-part-navigation\">Krmarjenje po besedilu</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: part.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"kate-part-selection\">Working with the Selection</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"kate-part-selection\">Delo z izborom</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: part.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-part-copy-and-paste\">Copying and Pasting Text</link>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-part-copy-and-paste\">Kopiranje in lepljenje besedila</"
"link>"

#. Tag: link
#: part.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-part-find-replace\">Finding and Replacing Text</link>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-part-find-replace\">Iskanje in zamenjava besedila</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: part.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"kate-part-bookmarks\">Using Bookmarks</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"kate-part-bookmarks\">Uporaba zaznamkov</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: part.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatically Wrapping Text"
msgstr "Samodejno prelivanje besedila"

#. Tag: link
#: part.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"kate-part-autoindent\">Using automatic indenting</link>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-part-autoindent\">Uporaba samodejnega zamika</link>"

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Navigating in the Text</title>"
msgstr "<title>Krmarjenje po besedilu</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Moving around in the text in &kappname; is similar to most graphical text "
"editors. You move the cursor using the arrow keys and the &PgUp;, &PgDn;, "
"&Home; and &End; keys in combination with the &Ctrl; and &Shift; modifiers. "
"The &Shift; key is always used to generate a selection, while the &Ctrl; key "
"has different effects on different keys:"
msgstr ""
"Premikanje po besedilu v &kappname; je podoben večini grafičnih "
"urejevalnikov besedil. Kazalec premikate s puščičnimi tipkami in &PgUp;, "
"&PgDn;, &Home; in &End; tipke v kombinaciji s tipko &Ctrl; in &Shift; "
"modifikatorji. &Shift; tipka se vedno uporablja za ustvarjanje izbire, "
"medtem ko &Ctrl; tipka ima različne učinke na različne tipke:"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For the &Up; and &Down; keys it means scroll rather than move the cursor."
msgstr "Za &Up; in &Down; tipke pomeni pomikanje in ne premikanje kazalke."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For the &Left; and &Right; keys it means skip words rather than characters."
msgstr "Za &Left; in &Right; tipke pomeni preskakovanje besed in ne znakov."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For the &PgUp; and &PgDn; keys it means move to the visible edge of the view "
"rather than browse."
msgstr ""
"Za &PgUp; in &PgDn; tipke pomeni pomik na vidni rob pogleda namesto brskanja."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For the &Home; and &End; keys it means move to the beginning or end of the "
"document rather than the beginning or end of the line."
msgstr ""
"Za &Home; in &Konec; tipke pomeni pomik na začetek ali konec dokumenta in ne "
"na začetek ali konec vrstice."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kappname; also provides you with a way to quickly jump to a matching brace "
"or parenthesis: place the cursor on the inside of a parenthesis or brace "
"character, and press <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>6</keycap></"
"keycombo> to jump to the matching parenthesis or brace."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; omogoča tudi hiter skok na ujemajoči se oklepaj ali oklepaj: "
"postavite kazalec na notranjo stran znaka oklepaja ali oklepaja in "
"pritisnite <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>6</keycap></keycombo> za "
"skok na ujemajoči se oklepaj ali oklepaj."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition you can use <link linkend=\"kate-part-bookmarks\">bookmarks</"
"link> to quickly jump to positions that you define on your own."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega lahko uporabite <link linkend=\"kate-part-bookmarks\">zaznamke</"
"link> za hiter skok na položaje, ki jih določite sami."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Working with the Selection</title>"
msgstr "<title>Delo z izborom</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are two basic ways of selecting text in &kappname;: using the mouse, "
"and using the keyboard."
msgstr ""
"Obstajata dva osnovna načina izbiranja besedila v &kappname;: z miško in s "
"tipkovnico."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To select using the mouse, hold down the &LMB; while dragging the mouse "
"cursor from where the selection should start, to the desired end point. The "
"text gets selected as you drag."
msgstr ""
"Za izbiro z miško pridržite tipko &LMB; medtem ko vlečete kazalec miške od "
"mesta, kjer naj se izbira začne, do želene končne točke. Besedilo se izbere "
"med vlečenjem."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "Double-clicking a word will select that word."
msgstr "Če dvakrat kliknete besedo, jo izberete."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "Triple-clicking in a line will select the entire line."
msgstr "Če trikrat kliknete v vrstico, boste izbrali celotno vrstico."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid "If &Shift; is held down while clicking, text will be selected:"
msgstr "Če &Shift; med klikanjem držite pritisnjeno, bo izbrano besedilo:"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If nothing is already selected, from the text cursor position to the mouse "
"cursor position."
msgstr ""
"Če še ni nič izbrano, od položaja kazalca besedila do položaja kazalca miške."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If there is a selection, from and including that selection to the mouse "
"cursor position."
msgstr ""
"Če obstaja izbor, od in vključno s tem izborom do položaja kazalca miške."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When selecting text by dragging the mouse, the selected text is copied to "
"the clipboard, and can be pasted by clicking the middle mouse button in the "
"editor, or in any other application to which you want to paste the text."
msgstr ""
"Pri izbiri besedila z vlečenjem miške se izbrano besedilo prekopira v "
"odložišče in ga lahko prilepite s klikom na srednji gumb miške v "
"urejevalniku ali v kateri koli drugi aplikaciji, v katero želite prilepiti "
"besedilo."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To select using the keyboard, hold down the &Shift; key while using the "
"navigation keys (Arrow keys, &PgUp;, &PgDn;, &Home; and &End;, possibly in "
"combination with &Ctrl; to extend the move of the text cursor)."
msgstr ""
"Za izbiro s tipkovnico pridržite &Shift; med uporabo navigacijskih tipk "
"(puščice, &PgUp;, &PgDn;, &Home; in &End;, po možnosti v kombinaciji s "
"&Ctrl; za podaljšanje premika besedilnega kazalca)."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See also the section <link linkend=\"kate-part-navigation\">Navigating in "
"the Text</link> in this chapter."
msgstr ""
"Glejte tudi razdelek <link linkend=\"kate-part-navigation\">Krmarjenje po "
"besedilu</link> v tem poglavju."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To <action>Copy</action> the current selection, use the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu item or the keyboard shortcut (defaults to <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"Če želite <action>Kopirati</action> trenutni izbor, uporabite menijski "
"element <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kopiraj</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali bližnjico na tipkovnici (privzeto na <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>)."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To <action>Deselect</action> the current selection, use the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Deselect</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu item, or the keyboard shortcut (default is <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo>), or click with the "
"&LMB; in the editor."
msgstr ""
"Za <action>Preklic</action> trenutnega izbora uporabite menijski element "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prekliči izbor</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali bližnjico na tipkovnici (privzeto je <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo>) ali kliknite z "
"&LMB; v urejevalniku."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Block Selection"
msgstr "Uporaba izbire blokov"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When Block Selection is enabled, you can make <quote>vertical selections</"
"quote> in the text, meaning selecting limited columns from multiple lines. "
"This is handy for working with tab separated lines for example."
msgstr ""
"Ko je omogočena izbira blokov, lahko naredite <quote>navpične izbire</quote> "
"v besedilu, kar pomeni, da izberete omejene stolpce iz več vrstic. To je "
"priročno na primer za delo z vrsticami, ločenimi s tabulatorji."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Block Selection can be toggled using the <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Block Selection Mode</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. The "
"default keyboard shortcut is <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;"
"<keycap>B</keycap> </keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Izbiro bloka lahko preklopite z menijsko postavko "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Način izbire bloka</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Privzeta bližnjica na tipkovnici je <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>B</keycap> </keycombo>."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Overwrite Selection"
msgstr "Uporaba Prepiši izbor"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If Overwrite Selection is enabled, typing or pasting text into the selection "
"will cause the selected text to be replaced. If not enabled, new text will "
"be added at the position of the text cursor."
msgstr ""
"Če je omogočena možnost Prepiši izbor, bo vnos ali lepljenje besedila v "
"izbor povzročilo zamenjavo izbranega besedila. Če ni omogočeno, bo novo "
"besedilo dodano na položaj besedilnega kazalca."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid "Overwrite Selection is enabled by default."
msgstr "Prepiši izbor je privzeto omogočen."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the setting for this option, use the <link linkend=\"pref-edit-"
"cursor-selection\">Cursor &amp; Selection</link> page of the <link linkend="
"\"config-dialog\">Configuration Dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti nastavitev za to možnost, uporabite <link linkend="
"\"pref-edit-cursor-selection\">Kazalka &amp; Stran za izbiro</link> v <link "
"linkend=\"config-dialog\">konfiguracijskem pogovornem oknu</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Persistent Selection"
msgstr "Uporaba trajne izbire"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When Persistent Selection is enabled, typing characters or moving the cursor "
"will not cause the Selection to become deselected. This means that you can "
"move the cursor away from the selection and type text."
msgstr ""
"Ko je vztrajna izbira omogočena, vnašanje znakov ali premikanje kazalca ne "
"bo povzročilo preklica izbire. To pomeni, da lahko premaknete kazalec stran "
"od izbora in vnesete besedilo."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "Persistent Selection is disabled by default."
msgstr "Trajna izbira je privzeto onemogočena."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Persistent Selection can be enabled in the <link linkend=\"pref-edit-cursor-"
"selection\">Cursor &amp; Selection</link> page of the <link linkend=\"config-"
"dialog\">Configuration Dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Vztrajno izbiro lahko omogočite v <link linkend=\"pref-edit-cursor-selection"
"\">Kazalka &amp; Stran za izbiro</link> v <link linkend=\"config-dialog"
"\">konfiguracijskem pogovornem oknu</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If Persistent Selection and Overwrite Selection are both enabled, typing or "
"pasting text when the text cursor is inside the selection will cause it to "
"be replaced and deselected."
msgstr ""
"Če sta omogočeni tako Trajna izbira kot Prepiši izbiro, bo vnašanje ali "
"lepljenje besedila, ko je besedilni kazalka znotraj izbora, povzročilo "
"njegovo zamenjavo in preklic izbire."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Copying and Pasting Text</title>"
msgstr "<title>Kopiranje in lepljenje besedila</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To copy text, select it and use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. Additionally, "
"selecting text with the mouse will cause selected text to be copied to the X "
"selection."
msgstr ""
"Če želite kopirati besedilo, ga izberite in uporabite menijsko postavko "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. Poleg tega bo izbira besedila z miško povzročila kopiranje "
"izbranega besedila v izbor X."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To paste the text currently in the clipboard, use the <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu "
"item."
msgstr ""
"Če želite prilepiti besedilo, ki je trenutno v odložišču, uporabite menijsko "
"postavko <menuchoice> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prilepi</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally, text selected with the mouse may be pasted by clicking the "
"&MMB; at the desired position."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega lahko besedilo, izbrano z miško, prilepite s klikom na &MMB; na "
"želenem položaju."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are using the &kde; desktop, you can retrieve earlier copied text "
"from any application using the &klipper; icon in the system tray."
msgstr ""
"Če uporabljate &kde; namizja, lahko prej kopirano besedilo pridobite iz "
"katere koli aplikacije z uporabo &klipper; ikono v sistemski vrstici."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Finding and Replacing Text</title>"
msgstr "<title>Iskanje in zamenjava besedila</title>"

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Search and Replace Bars"
msgstr "Vrstici za iskanje in zamenjavo"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kappname; has an incremental search bar and a power search and replace bar, "
"which offers the means of entering a replacement string along with a few "
"extra options."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; ima inkrementalno vrstico za iskanje in zmogljivo vrstico za "
"iskanje in zamenjavo, ki ponuja sredstva za vnos nadomestnega niza skupaj z "
"nekaj dodatnimi možnostmi."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid "The bars offer the following common options:"
msgstr "Vrstice ponujajo naslednje običajne možnosti:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: part.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find"
msgstr "Poišči"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:285
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is where to enter the search string. The interpretation of the string "
"depends on some of the options described below."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj vnesete iskalni niz. Razlaga niza je odvisna od nekaterih spodaj "
"opisanih možnosti."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: part.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid "Match case"
msgstr "Primer ujemanja"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, the search will be limited to entries that match the case (upper "
"or lower) of each of the characters in the search pattern."
msgstr ""
"Če je omogočeno, bo iskanje omejeno na vnose, ki se ujemajo z velikimi ali "
"malimi črkami vsakega od znakov v iskalnem vzorcu."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid "The power search and replace bar offers some additional options:"
msgstr "Močna vrstica za iskanje in zamenjavo ponuja nekaj dodatnih možnosti:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: part.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plain Text"
msgstr "Golo besedilo"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:307
#, no-c-format
msgid "Literally match any occurrence of the search string."
msgstr "Dobesedno ujemanje s katero koli pojavitvijo iskalnega niza."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: part.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid "Whole Words"
msgstr "Cele besede"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If selected, the search will only match if there is a word boundary at both "
"ends of the string matching, meaning not an alphanumeric character - either "
"some other visible character or a line end."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbrano, se bo iskanje ujemalo le, če je na obeh koncih ujemajočega se "
"niza besedna meja, kar pomeni, da ni alfanumerični znak – bodisi kakšen drug "
"viden znak ali konec vrstice."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: part.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid "Escape Sequences"
msgstr "Ubežna zaporedja"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If selected, the <guibutton>Add</guibutton> menuitem at the bottom of the "
"context menu of the text boxes will be enabled and allows you to add escape "
"sequences to the search pattern from a predefined list."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbrano, bo menijski element <guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton> na dnu "
"kontekstnega menija besedilnih polj omogočen in vam omogoča dodajanje "
"ubežnih zaporedij iskalnemu vzorcu iz vnaprej določenega seznama."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: part.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid "Regular Expression"
msgstr "Regularni izraz"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If selected, the search string is interpreted as a regular expression. The "
"<guibutton>Add</guibutton> menuitem at the bottom of the context menu of the "
"text boxes will be enabled and allows you to add regular expression items to "
"the search pattern from a predefined list."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete, se iskalni niz interpretira kot regularni izraz. Menijski "
"element <guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton> na dnu kontekstnega menija besedilnih "
"polj bo omogočen in vam bo omogočil dodajanje postavk regularnega izraza "
"iskalnemu vzorcu iz vnaprej določenega seznama."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:339
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See <link linkend=\"regular-expressions\">Regular Expressions</link> for "
"more on these."
msgstr ""
"Glejte <link linkend=\"regular-expressions\">Regularni izrazi</link> za več "
"o tem."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: part.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search in the selection only"
msgstr "Išči samo v izboru"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:347
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, the search and replace will be performed within the selected "
"text only."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno, bo iskanje in zamenjava izvedena samo znotraj izbranega "
"besedila."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: part.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find all"
msgstr "Najdi vse"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking this button highlights all matches in the document and shows the "
"number of found matches in a small popup."
msgstr ""
"Klik na ta gumb označi vse zadetke v dokumentu in prikaže število najdenih "
"zadetkov v majhnem pojavnem oknu."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid "Finding Text"
msgstr "Iskanje besedila"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:367
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To find text, launch the incremental search bar with <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> or from the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Če želite poiskati besedilo, zaženite inkrementalno iskalno vrstico s "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> ali iz "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Najdi ...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> element menija."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:371
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This opens the incremental search bar at the bottom of the editor window. On "
"the left side of the bar is a button with an icon to close the bar, followed "
"by a small text box for entering the search pattern."
msgstr ""
"To odpre vrstico za postopno iskanje na dnu okna urejevalnika. Na levi "
"strani vrstice je gumb z ikono za zapiranje vrstice, ki mu sledi majhno "
"besedilno polje za vnos iskalnega vzorca."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start entering the characters of your search pattern, the search "
"starts immediately. If there is a match in the text this is highlighted and "
"the background color of the entry field changes to light green. If the "
"search pattern does not match any string in the text, this is indicated by a "
"light red background color of the entry field."
msgstr ""
"Ko začnete vnašati znake iskalnega vzorca, se iskanje začne takoj. Če se "
"besedilo ujema, je to označeno in barva ozadja vnosnega polja se spremeni v "
"svetlo zeleno. Če se iskalni vzorec ne ujema z nobenim nizom v besedilu, je "
"to označeno s svetlo rdečo barvo ozadja vnosnega polja."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:378 part.docbook:422
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"arrow-up-"
"double-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> or "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"arrow-down-double-22.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> button to jump to the "
"next or previous match in the document."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"arrow-up-"
"double-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> ali "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"arrow-down-double-22.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> gumb za skok na "
"naslednje ali prejšnje ujemanje v dokumentu."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Matches in the document are highlighted even when you close the search bar. "
"To clear this highlighting, press the &Esc; key."
msgstr ""
"Ujemanja v dokumentu so označena tudi, ko zaprete iskalno vrstico. Če želite "
"počistiti to označevanje, pritisnite &Esc; ključ."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:384
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can choose whether the search should be case sensitive. Selecting "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"format-text-"
"superscript-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> will "
"limit finds to entries that match the case (upper or lower) of each of the "
"characters in the search pattern."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko, ali naj iskanje razlikuje med velikimi in malimi črkami. Če "
"izberete <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"format-text-"
"superscript-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>, "
"boste omejili najdbe na vnose, ki se ujemajo z velikimi ali malimi črkami ) "
"vsakega od znakov v iskalnem vzorcu."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:388
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"configure-"
"shortcuts-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> button "
"at the right side of the incremental search bar to switch to the power "
"search and replace bar."
msgstr "Za preklop na vrstica za iskanje in zamenjavo moči."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To repeat the last find operation, if any, without calling the incremental "
"search bar, use <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul"
"\"><keycap>F3</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Find Next</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or "
"<menuchoice><shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F3</"
"keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Find "
"Previous</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ponoviti zadnjo operacijo iskanja, če obstaja, brez klica "
"prirastne vrstice za iskanje, uporabite <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo "
"action=\"simul\"><keycap>F3</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu >Uredi</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Poišči naslednje</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali "
"<menuchoice><shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F3</"
"keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Poišči "
"prejšnje</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid "Replacing Text"
msgstr "Zamenjava besedila"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To replace text, launch the power search and replace bar using the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Replace</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> command, or the <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</"
"keycap></keycombo> shortcut."
msgstr ""
"Če želite zamenjati besedilo, zaženite zmogljivo vrstico za iskanje in "
"zamenjavo z ukazom <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Zamenjaj</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl; Bližnjica <keycap>R</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:412
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the upper left side of the bar is a button with an icon to close the bar, "
"followed by a small combo box for entering the search pattern. The box "
"remembers recently used patterns."
msgstr ""
"Na zgornji levi strani vrstice je gumb z ikono za zapiranje vrstice, ki mu "
"sledi majhno kombinirano polje za vnos iskalnega vzorca. Škatla si zapomni "
"nedavno uporabljene vzorce."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can control the search mode by selecting the options <guilabel>Plain "
"Text</guilabel>, <guilabel>Whole Words</guilabel>, <guilabel>Escape "
"Sequences</guilabel> or <guilabel>Regular Expression</guilabel> from the "
"drop down box."
msgstr ""
"Način iskanja lahko nadzorujete tako, da izberete možnosti <guilabel>Navadno "
"besedilo</guilabel>, <guilabel>Cele besede</guilabel>, <guilabel>Ubežna "
"zaporedja</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Regularni izraz</guilabel> iz spustno "
"polje."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:418
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Escape sequences</guilabel> or <guilabel>Regular expression</"
"guilabel> are selected, the <guibutton>Add...</guibutton> menuitem at the "
"bottom of the context menu of the text boxes will be enabled and allows you "
"to add escape sequences or regular expression items to the search or replace "
"pattern from predefined lists."
msgstr ""
"Če so izbrana <guilabel>Ubežna zaporedja</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Regularni "
"izraz</guilabel>, bo omogočen menijski element <guibutton>Dodaj ...</"
"guibutton> na dnu priročnega menija besedilnih polj in vam omogoča dodajanje "
"ubežnih zaporedij ali postavk regularnega izraza v vzorec iskanja ali "
"zamenjave iz vnaprej določenih seznamov."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:426
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the text to replace with in the text box labeled <guilabel>Replace</"
"guilabel> and click the <guibutton>Replace</guibutton> button to replace "
"only the highlighted text or the <guibutton>Replace All</guibutton> button "
"to replace the search text in the whole document."
msgstr ""
"V besedilno polje z oznako <guilabel>Zamenjaj</guilabel> vnesite besedilo, s "
"katerim želite zamenjati, in kliknite gumb <guibutton>Zamenjaj</guibutton>, "
"da zamenjate samo označeno besedilo, ali gumb <guibutton>Zamenjaj vse</"
"guibutton>, da zamenjajte iskalno besedilo v celotnem dokumentu."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:430
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can modify the search and replace behavior by selecting different "
"options at the bottom of the bar. Selecting "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"format-text-"
"superscript-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> will "
"limit finds to entries that match the case (upper or lower) of each of the "
"characters in the search pattern. <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata "
"fileref=\"edit-select-all-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject> will search and replace within the current selection "
"only. The <guilabel>Find All</guilabel> button highlights all matches in the "
"document and shows the number of found matches in a small popup."
msgstr ""
"Obnašanje iskanja in zamenjave lahko spremenite tako, da izberete različne "
"možnosti na dnu vrstice. Če izberete "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"format-text-"
"superscript-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>, "
"boste omejili iskanje na vnose, ki se ujemajo z velikimi ali malimi črkami ) "
"vsakega od znakov v iskalnem vzorcu. "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-select-all-22.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> bo iskal in zamenjal "
"samo znotraj trenutnega izbora. Gumb <guilabel>Najdi vse</guilabel> označi "
"vse zadetke v dokumentu in prikaže število najdenih zadetkov v majhnem "
"pojavnem oknu."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:440
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"configure-"
"shortcuts-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> button "
"at the right side of the power search and replace bar to switch to the "
"incremental search bar."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"configure-"
"shortcuts-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> na "
"desni strani zmogljive vrstice za iskanje in zamenjavo za preklopite na "
"vrstico za postopno iskanje."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:445
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are using a regular expression to find the text to replace, you can "
"employ backreferences to reuse text captured in parenthesized subpatterns of "
"the expression."
msgstr ""
"Če uporabljate regularni izraz za iskanje besedila za zamenjavo, lahko "
"uporabite povratne reference za ponovno uporabo besedila, zajetega v "
"podvzorcih izraza v oklepajih."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See <link linkend=\"regular-expressions\">Regular Expressions</link> for "
"more on those."
msgstr ""
"Glejte <link linkend=\"regular-expressions\">Regularni izrazi</link> za več "
"o tem."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:451
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can do <command>find</command>, <command>replace</command> and "
"<command>ifind</command> (incremental search) from the <link linkend="
"\"advanced-editing-tools-commandline\">command line</link>."
msgstr ""
"Izvedete lahko <command>najdi</command>, <command>zamenjaj</command> in "
"<command>inajdi</command> (inkrementalno iskanje) z ukazom <link linkend="
"\"advanced-editing-tools-commandline\"> vrstica</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:461
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Using Bookmarks</title>"
msgstr "<title>Uporaba zaznamkov</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:463
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The bookmarks feature allows you to mark certain lines, to be able to easily "
"find them again."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija zaznamkov vam omogoča, da označite določene vrstice, da jih lahko "
"znova enostavno najdete."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:466
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can set or remove a bookmark in a line in two ways:"
msgstr "Zaznamek v vrstici lahko nastavite ali odstranite na dva načina:"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:470
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Move the insertion cursor to the line and activate the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu><guimenuitem>Set Bookmark</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>B</"
"keycap></keycombo>) command."
msgstr ""
"Kazalec za vstavljanje premaknite v vrstico in aktivirajte "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nastavi zaznamek</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>B</"
"keycap></keycombo>)."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:476
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click in the Icon Border next to the line."
msgstr "Kliknite obrobo ikone poleg črte."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:481
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Bookmarks are available in the <guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> menu. The "
"individual bookmarks are available as menu items, labeled with the line "
"number of the line with the bookmark, and the first few characters of the "
"text in the line. To move the insertion cursor to the beginning of a "
"bookmarked line, open the menu and select the bookmark."
msgstr ""
"Zaznamki so na voljo v meniju <guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu>. Posamezni "
"zaznamki so na voljo kot menijski elementi, označeni s številko vrstice "
"vrstice z zaznamkom in prvih nekaj znakov besedila v vrstici. Če želite "
"premakniti kazalec za vstavljanje na začetek označene vrstice, odprite meni "
"in izberite zaznamek."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:488
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To quickly move between bookmarks or to the next/previous bookmark, use the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu><guimenuitem>Next</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&PgDn;</keycombo>) or "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu><guimenuitem>Previous</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&PgUp;</"
"keycombo>) commands."
msgstr ""
"Za hitro premikanje med zaznamki ali na naslednji/prejšnji zaznamek "
"uporabite <menuchoice><guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu><guimenuitem>Naprej</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&PgDn;</"
"keycombo>) ali <menuchoice> <guimenu>Zaznamki</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Prejšnji</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Alt;&PgUp;</keycombo>) ukazi."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:498
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatically Wrapping text"
msgstr "Samodejno prelivanje besedila"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:500
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This feature allows you to have the text formatted in a very simple way: the "
"text will be wrapped, so that no lines exceed a maximum number of characters "
"per line, unless there is a longer string of non-whitespace characters."
msgstr ""
"Ta funkcija vam omogoča, da besedilo oblikujete na zelo preprost način: "
"besedilo bo prelojeno, tako da nobena vrstica ne bo presegla največjega "
"števila znakov na vrstico, razen če obstaja daljši niz znakov, ki niso "
"presledki."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To enable/disable it, check/uncheck the <guibutton>Static Word Wrap</"
"guibutton> checkbox in the <link linkend=\"pref-word-wrap\">edit page</link> "
"of the <link linkend=\"config-dialog\">configuration dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Če ga želite omogočiti/onemogočiti, označite/počistite potrditveno polje "
"<guibutton>Statični prelom besed</guibutton> na <link linkend=\"pref-word-"
"wrap\">strani za urejanje</link> v <link linkend=\"config- dialog"
"\">konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:507
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To set the maximum line width (maximum characters per line), use the <link "
"linkend=\"pref-wrap-words-at\"><guibutton>Wrap Words At</guibutton></link> "
"option in the <link linkend=\"pref-edit\">Editing</link> page of the <link "
"linkend=\"config-dialog\">configuration dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite nastaviti največjo širino vrstice (največje število znakov na "
"vrstico), uporabite možnost <link linkend=\"pref-wrap-words-at"
"\"><guibutton>Prelomi besede v</guibutton></link> v Stran<link linkend="
"\"pref-edit\">Urejanje</link> v <link linkend=\"config-dialog"
"\">konfiguracijskem pogovornem oknu</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:512
#, no-c-format
msgid "If enabled, it has the following effects:"
msgstr "Če je omogočeno, ima naslednje učinke:"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:516
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"While typing, the editor will automatically insert a hard line break after "
"the last whitespace character at a position before the maximum line width is "
"reached."
msgstr ""
"Med tipkanjem bo urejevalnik samodejno vstavil trdi prelom vrstice za "
"zadnjim presledkom na mestu, preden je dosežena največja širina vrstice."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:518
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"While loading a document, the editor will wrap the text in a similar way, so "
"that no lines are longer than the maximum line width, if they contain any "
"whitespace allowing that."
msgstr ""
"Med nalaganjem dokumenta bo urejevalnik prelil besedilo na podoben način, "
"tako da nobena vrstica ni daljša od največje širine vrstice, če vsebuje "
"presledek, ki to omogoča."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:524
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is currently no way to set word wrap for document types, or even to "
"enable or disable the feature on a per document level. This will be fixed in "
"a future version of &kappname;."
msgstr ""
"Trenutno ni mogoče nastaviti prelivanja besed za vrste dokumentov ali celo "
"omogočiti ali onemogočiti funkcijo na ravni dokumenta. To bo popravljeno v "
"prihodnji različici &kappname;."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:530
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Using automatic indenting</title>"
msgstr "<title>Uporaba samodejnega zamika</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:532
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kappname;s editor component supports a variety of autoindenting modes, "
"designed for different text formats. You can pick from the available modes "
"using the <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guisubmenu>Indentation</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> menu. The autoindent modules also provide a "
"function <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Format "
"Indentation</guimenuitem></menuchoice> which will recalculate the "
"indentation of the selected or current line. Thus, you may reindent your "
"entire document by selecting all the text and activating that action."
msgstr ""
"Komponenta urejevalnika &kappname; podpira različne načine samodejnega "
"zamika, zasnovane za različne formate besedila. Izbirate lahko med "
"razpoložljivimi načini z uporabo menija <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Zamik</guisubmenu></menuchoice>. Moduli za samodejni "
"zamik nudijo tudi funkcijo <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Oblika zamika</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, ki bo znova "
"izračunala zamik izbrane ali trenutne vrstice. Tako lahko celoten dokument "
"ponovno zamaknete tako, da izberete celotno besedilo in aktivirate to "
"dejanje."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:541
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All the indent modes use the indentation related settings in the active "
"document."
msgstr ""
"Vsi načini zamika uporabljajo nastavitve, povezane z zamikom, v aktivnem "
"dokumentu."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:544
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can set all sorts of configuration variables, including those related to "
"indentation using <link linkend=\"config-variables\">Document Variables</"
"link> and <link linkend=\"pref-open-save-modes-filetypes\">File types</link>."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite lahko vse vrste konfiguracijskih spremenljivk, vključno s tistimi, "
"ki so povezane z zamikom, z uporabo <link linkend=\"config-variables"
"\">spremenljivk dokumenta</link> in <link linkend=\"pref-open-save-modes-"
"filetypes\">vrst datotek </link>."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:551
#, no-c-format
msgid "Available Autoindent Modes"
msgstr "Razpoložljivi načini samodejnega zamika"

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:554
#, no-c-format
msgid "None"
msgstr "Noben"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:555
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting this mode turns automatic indenting off entirely."
msgstr "Če izberete ta način, samodejno zamikanje popolnoma izklopite."

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:560
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normal"
msgstr "Normalno"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:561
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This indenter simply keeps the indentation similar to the previous line with "
"any content other than whitespace. You can combine this with using the "
"indent and unindent actions for indenting to your own taste."
msgstr ""
"Ta zamik preprosto ohrani zamik, podoben prejšnji vrstici, s katero koli "
"vsebino, razen presledkov. To lahko kombinirate z dejanji zamikanja in "
"odstranjevanja zamikov po lastnem okusu."

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:567
#, no-c-format
msgid "C Style"
msgstr "C slog"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:568
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An indenter for C and similar languages, such as C++, C#, &Java;, "
"&javascript; and so on. This indenter will not work with scripting languages "
"such as Perl or PHP."
msgstr ""
"Zamik za C in podobne jezike, kot so C++, C#, &Java;, &javascript; in tako "
"naprej. Ta zamik ne bo deloval s skriptnimi jeziki, kot sta Perl ali PHP."

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:574
#, no-c-format
msgid "Haskell"
msgstr "Haskell"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:575
#, no-c-format
msgid "An indenter for the functional programming language Haskell."
msgstr "Zamik za funkcijski programski jezik Haskell."

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lilypond"
msgstr "Lilypond"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:581
#, no-c-format
msgid "An indenter for the Lilypond notation language for music."
msgstr "Zamik za notni jezik Lilypond za glasbo."

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:586
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lisp"
msgstr "Lisp"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:587
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An indenter specifically for the Lisp scripting language and Lisp dialects."
msgstr "Indender posebej za skriptni jezik Lisp in narečja Lisp."

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:593
#, no-c-format
msgid "Python"
msgstr "Python"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:594
#, no-c-format
msgid "An indenter specifically for the python scripting language."
msgstr "Indender posebej za skriptni jezik python."

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:599
#, no-c-format
msgid "XML Style"
msgstr "Slog XML"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:600
#, no-c-format
msgid "An indenter specifically for XML like languages."
msgstr "Indender posebej za jezike, podobne XML."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:609
#, no-c-format
msgid "Line Modification Indicators"
msgstr "Indikatorji spremembe vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:611
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kappname;'s line modification indicators let you easily see what you have "
"recently changed in a file. By default, saved changes are indicated by a "
"green bar to the left of a document, while unsaved changes are indicated by "
"an orange bar."
msgstr ""
"Indikatorji spreminjanja vrstice &kappname; vam omogočajo, da preprosto "
"vidite, kaj ste nedavno spremenili v datoteki. Privzeto so shranjene "
"spremembe označene z zeleno vrstico na levi strani dokumenta, medtem ko so "
"neshranjene spremembe označene z oranžno vrstico."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:619
#, no-c-format
msgid "Line Modification Indicators in action."
msgstr "Indikatorji spreminjanja črte v akciji."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:623
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can change the colors used in the <link linkend=\"prefcolors"
"\"><guilabel>Fonts &amp; Colors</guilabel> configuration panel</link>, or "
"you can disable this feature completely in the <link linkend=\"appearance-"
"borders\"><guilabel>Borders</guilabel> tab of the <guilabel>Appearance</"
"guilabel> configuration panel</link>."
msgstr ""
"Spremenite lahko barve, uporabljene v <link linkend=\"prefcolors"
"\"><guilabel>Pisave &amp; Barve</guilabel>konfiguracijska plošča</link>, ali "
"pa lahko to funkcijo popolnoma onemogočite na zavihku <link linkend="
"\"appearance-borders\"><guilabel>Obrobe</guilabel> v <guilabel>Videzu</"
"guilabel> konfiguracijska plošča</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:632
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Scrollbar Minimap"
msgstr "Minikarta drsnega traku"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:634
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kappname;'s Scrollbar Minimap displays a preview of documents in place of "
"the scrollbar. The currently visible portion of the document is highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Minikarta drsnega traku &kappname; prikaže predogled dokumentov namesto "
"drsnega traku. Trenutno vidni del dokumenta je označen."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:641
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Scrollbar Minimap shows a preview of the &kate; source code."
msgstr ""
"Minikarta drsnega traku prikazuje predogled datoteke &kate; izvorna koda."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:646
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can temporarily enable or disable the minimap by selecting "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>View Scrollbar Minimap</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> or permanently in <link linkend=\"appearance-"
"borders\">the Appearance section of &kappname;'s configuration</link>."
msgstr ""
"Minimap lahko začasno omogočite ali onemogočite tako, da izberete "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Ogled drsnega traku "
"Minimap</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali trajno v <link linkend=\"appearance-"
"borders\">Videz razdelek konfiguracije &kappname;</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:654
#, no-c-format
msgid "Multiple cursors"
msgstr "Več kazalk"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:656
#, no-c-format
msgid "Multiple cursor support was introduced with version 5.93 of katepart."
msgstr "Podpora za več kazalk je bila predstavljena z različico katepart 5.93."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:659
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating multiple cursors"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje več kazalk"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:662
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create them via mouse, use &Alt; + &LMB;. The modifier is configurable, "
"see <link linkend=\"multicursor-modifier-configure\">Configure multicursor "
"modifier</link>"
msgstr ""
"Če jih želite ustvariti z miško, uporabite &lt; + mLB;. Modifikator je "
"mogoče konfigurirati, glejte <link linkend=\"multicursor-modifier-configure"
"\">Konfigurirajte modifikator večkazalk</link>"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:664
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create via keyboard, press <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Up;</"
"keycombo> to create cursor above primary cursor and <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Down;</keycombo> to create cursor below. These shortcuts are "
"also configurable"
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje prek tipkovnice pritisnite <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"&Alt;&Up;</keycombo>, da ustvarite kazalko nad primarno kazalko, in "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Down;</keycombo> za ustvarite kazalko "
"spodaj. Te bližnjice je tudi mogoče konfigurirati"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:666
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create cursors out of a selection, first select some text and then press "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;&Alt;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo>. This "
"will create a cursor at the end of each line in selection."
msgstr ""
"Če želite iz izbora ustvariti kazalko, najprej izberite besedilo in nato "
"pritisnite <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;&Alt;<keycap>I</keycap></"
"keycombo>. To bo ustvarilo kazalko na koncu vsake vrstice v izboru."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:668
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> to find "
"the next occurrence of the word under cursor and select it + create a "
"cursor. If you want to skip the current word under cursor, press <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>K</keycap></keycombo> and it will mark the "
"currently selected word as skipped. When you press <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Alt;<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> again it will unselect the current "
"word and move to the next word."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo>, da "
"poiščete naslednjo pojavitev besede pod kazalcem in jo izberete + ustvarite "
"kazalka. Če želite preskočiti trenutno besedo pod kazalcem, pritisnite "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>K</keycap></keycombo> in trenutno "
"izbrano besedo bo označil kot preskočeno. Ko znova pritisnete <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo>, bo preklicala izbiro "
"trenutne besede in se premaknila na naslednjo besedo."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:671
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Shift;<keycap>J</keycap></"
"keycombo> to find all occurrences of the word under cursor and select them "
"with a cursor at the end of each selection. You can use <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> to cycle through the selected "
"words and use <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>K</keycap></keycombo> "
"to unselect any word as mentioned in the previous paragraph."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Shift;<keycap>J</keycap></"
"keycombo>, da poiščete vse pojavitve besede pod kazalko in jih izberete s "
"kazalko na koncu vsakega izbora. Uporabite lahko <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Alt;<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> za kroženje med izbranimi besedami in "
"uporabite <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>K</keycap ></keycombo> za "
"preklic izbire katere koli besede, kot je omenjeno v prejšnjem odstavku."

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:676
#, no-c-format
msgid "Working with multiple cursors"
msgstr "Delo z več kazalkami"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:677
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you have created a few cursors, you can perform most of the editing "
"operations on them as you would on a single cursor. For example, typing a "
"letter will type it for each cursor. Similarly you can perform text "
"transforms &eg;, capitalization for all the positions or selections."
msgstr ""
"Ko ustvarite nekaj kazalk, lahko na njih izvajate večino operacij urejanja, "
"kot bi to storili na enem samem kazalcu. Če na primer vtipkate črko, jo "
"boste vnesli za vsako kazalko. Podobno lahko izvajate transformacije "
"besedila &eg;, velike črke za vse položaje ali izbore."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:681
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sometimes you will want to remove cursors. To do so, you can &Alt; + &LMB; "
"on the cursor that you want to remove. If you just want to remove cursors on "
"lines that are empty, there is a ready-made action for it that will do it "
"for you. To invoke the action, open the Command Bar using <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo> and look for "
"<guimenuitem>Remove cursors from empty lines</guimenuitem> and hit &Enter;. "
"You can also configure a shortcut for this action."
msgstr ""
"Včasih boste želeli odstraniti kazalce. Če želite to narediti, lahko &Alt; + "
"&LMB; na kazalcu, ki ga želite odstraniti. Če samo želite odstraniti kazalce "
"na praznih vrsticah, je za to že pripravljeno dejanje, ki bo to storilo "
"namesto vas. Če želite priklicati dejanje, odprite ukazno vrstico s "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo> in "
"poiščite <guimenuitem>Odstrani kazalce iz praznih vrstic</guimenuitem> in "
"pritisnite &Enter;. Za to dejanje lahko konfigurirate tudi bližnjico."
